snippet.title: NoLimits 2 - Roller Coaster Simulation - Now Available
snippet.description:
NoLimits 2 is now available!  http://www.nolimitscoaster.com

The NoLimits Development Team wishes you a Merry Christmas. NoLimits 2 launches January 10th!. We are proud to show you meanwhile a couple of long takes using the film quality motion blur. You will see the new 4D coaster, the new dive coaster, the new suspended coaster, and the new flying coaster.
